-- Ex-Galleon Executive Settles SEC Tipping Suit for $1.75 Million
-- B y   P a t r i c i a   H u r t a d o
-- 2012-10-26T16:57:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-26/ex-galleon-executive-settles-sec-tipping-suit-for-1-75-million.html
Kris Chellam, a former Galleon Group
LLC executive, agreed to pay $1.75 million to settle a lawsuit
brought by the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission accusing
him of passing inside information to Raj Rajaratnam, the agency
said in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
